    <note>Zhao(1) Fang(2) [15217] Began as a civil official and later became a general. His wife, born Hu(1), was from a Jizhou, Jian lineage, and therefore probably related to Hu(1) Quan [10565], that segemented into a branch that moved to Tanzhou, Xiangtan county where they became a distinguished lineage (wangzu). Liu Zai, WJ, 35.7b-12b (wife, born Hu(1), who married him at age 22 and died in 1230 at age 78). Hunan TZ, 134.18a. CBD, 4, 3315-6.</note>
